{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/python/regex/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"hong_devlog","author":"hongdev","siteUrl":"https://hong-dev.github.io","comment":{"disqusShortName":"","utterances":"hong-dev/hong-dev.github.io"},"sponsor":{"buyMeACoffeeId":""}}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"27f1eec8-9ddc-5b97-800c-fc8c71fde682","excerpt":"Regular Expression, Regex, Regexp, 정규표현식 등으로 불리는 정규식 password validator 조건 영문 대문자, 소문자, 특수문자, 숫자 각 1개 이상씩 포함 최소 10자 이상","html":"<p>Regular Expression, Regex, Regexp, 정규표현식 등으로 불리는 정규식</p>\n<p>password validator 조건</p>\n<ul>\n<li>영문 대문자, 소문자, 특수문자, 숫자 각 1개 이상씩 포함</li>\n<li>최소 10자 이상</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> re\n\nre<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>match<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n  <span class=\"token string\">r'^(?=.*[A-Z])(?=.*[a-z])(?=.*\\d)(?=.*[!@#$%^&amp;*()_])[A-Za-z\\d!@#$%^&amp;*()_]{10,}'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  password\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"title":"정규표현식으로 비밀번호 유효성 검사: re.match","date":"June 02, 2020","category":"python","thumbnail":null}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/python/regex/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/commands/find_tree_grep/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"shell commands: find","category":"commands","draft":false}},"next":null}}}